node.text:
As part of our Back to ____ campaign, we're heading into the Fall with intention and focus on what’s important to us: positive mental health. So we donated $200,000 to @JedFoundation's Set to Go program. 

But PINK, where does your donation go? 🤔 Glad you asked! 

Preparing for college is more than just academics and testing. Being emotionally ready creates the greatest opportunity for success! These funds help students with finding the right college fit, developing important emotional and life skills, increasing knowledge about important health issues for guidance about adjusting to life at college, and so much more!!
